# App configuration example
# These settings are typically set via environment variables:
#
# Required:
#   APP_TLS_CERT     - Path to TLS certificate
#   APP_TLS_KEY      - Path to TLS private key
#   APP_CA_CERT      - Path to CA certificate (for client verification)
#
# Optional:
#   APP_PORT         - Server port (default: 8443)
#   APP_AUTH_MODE    - Authentication mode: apikey, basic, or mtls (default: apikey)
#   APP_API_KEY      - API key for apikey auth mode
#   APP_BASIC_AUTH_USER - Username for basic auth mode
#   APP_BASIC_AUTH_PASS - Password for basic auth mode
#
# Service API keys (override yaml config):
#   SONARR_URL       - Sonarr instance URL
#   SONARR_API_KEY   - Sonarr API key
#   RADARR_URL       - Radarr instance URL
#   RADARR_API_KEY   - Radarr API key
